\par 5. M\'e9t x\'dd nghi\'d6p c\'f1a m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t s\'cf kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec coi l\'b5 c\'e3 c\'ac s\'eb th\'ad\'eang tr\'f3 \'eb N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t kia n\'d5u x\'dd nghi\'d6p \'ae\'e3 ch\'d8 th\'f9c hi\'d6n ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9
ng kinh doanh t\'b9i N\'ad\'edc kia th\'abng qua m\'e9t \'ae\'b9i l\'fd m\'abi gi\'edi, m\'e9t \'ae\'b9i l\'fd hoa h\'e5ng ho\'c6c b\'cat k\'fa m\'e9t \'ae\'b9i l\'fd n\'b5o c\'e3 t\'ad c\'b8ch \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp v\'edi \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e8
